node.text:
Guys, a lot of you asking me how is it going with my exclusive Photobook📸📕 which I've been working on during the whole summer.
First of all don't worry, I'm going to make a release at the beginning of the next month! 😉 The printing agency caused me a lot of complications and sucked a lot of blood out of me for no reason, that's why it's delayed🤦🏼‍♀️😑
Buuut... as a compensation for this delay I'm going to add one more sensual extra photoset which I'm going to shoot next days! 😏🔥 
Meanwhile here are my today's photos in orange bodysuit to encourage you a little 🥰

#ootd #photobook
